  "text": "The present work deals with the characterisation of such wires made of Ti and an Al alloy (AA5049). In the case of sheet materials, it has been shown that such a material composition is processable by ARB [CITATION_1] . Furthermore, a reaction annealing allows the fabrication of a γ-TiAl sheet. In the present study the processing of wires is presented with a more detailed view at mechanical properties and the evolution of the microstructure at larger deformation strains. Composite wires with an ufg microstructure are produced and their microstructure-properties relationship is investigated by means of electron backscatter diffraction (EBSD) analysis and tensile testings.",
  "correct_citation": {
